  levelName: "m\xE0n 1"
  introLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Th\u1EDDi ti\u1EBFt ng\xE0y h\xF4m n\xE0y th\u1EADt \u0111\u1EB9p nh\u1EC9
      Shadow, m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xEAn th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 c\u1EA3 r\u1ED3i
      \u0111\u1EC3 m\xECnh t\xF4i l\u1EA1i canh l\xE0ng n\xE0y, Kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt
      khi n\xE0o h\u1ECD quay l\u1EA1i nh\u1EC9."
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "hahaha mi hi\u1EC3u ta n\xF3i g\xEC \xE0?"
  - speaker: Shadow
    text: "g\xE2u g\xE2u !"
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "Ch\u1EDD  \u0111\xE3 th\u1EE9 g\xEC \u0111\u1EB1ng kia  \u0111ang chuy\u1EC3n
      \u0111\u1ED9ng v\u1EADy?\r\nC\u1EA9n th\u1EADn Shadow!!!\r\n"
  outroLines:
  - speaker: Arin
    text: "K\u1EBFt th\xFAc r\u1ED3i sao ?. Ch\xFAng l\xE0 th\u1EE9 qu\xE1i d\u1ECB
      g\xEC v\u1EADy ?? Slime sao? Tr\xEAn th\u1EF1c t\u1EBF ch\xFAng  \u0111\xE1ng
      l\u1EBD kh\xF4ng t\u1ED3n t\u1EA1i \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c ch\u1EE9??"
